@startuml UC-01-Auth
title Bieu do Use Case - Xac thuc & Phien dang nhap

skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam usecaseBorderColor #2C7BB6
skinparam usecaseBackgroundColor #EEF6FF
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #888
skinparam ArrowColor #444
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

left to right direction

actor "Khach vang lai (Guest)"     as Guest
actor "Nguoi dung da dang ky"      as User
actor "Client App\n(interceptor)"  as Client

rectangle "Auth & Session System" {

    usecase "Dang ky tai khoan\n(email + username + password)" as UC1
    usecase "Dang nhap\n(tra ve access token + refresh cookie)" as UC2
    usecase "Dang xuat\n(revoke refresh token)"                 as UC3
    usecase "Lam moi token\n(rotate refresh token)"             as UC4
    usecase "Ep dang xuat\n(khi refresh token loi)"            as UC5

    UC4 .> UC2  : <<extend>>
    UC5 .> UC4  : <<extend>>
}

Guest  --> UC1
Guest  --> UC2
User   --> UC2
User   --> UC3
Client --> UC4
Client --> UC5

@enduml
